{"tid":1064773,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警方從來無公開過武力使用手則，唔好亂信網上謠言","createTime":"2019-03-16T19:29:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T19:59:39.000Z","uid":27530,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c8dfa0c078a6a1d25029ed96ea105b3c2b409275","tid":1064773,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T19:29:43.000Z","msg":"最近，我係網上見到有啲傻仔話，警察有指引話１）開槍要打最大面積及２）可使用高一級武力，仲ＱＵＯＴＥ埋警察通例第２９章，我當堂嚇一跳，然後就得啖笑。<br />\n<br />\n大家可以睇下面張圖，警方網頁係證明佢無公開過第２９章或武力使用手則。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家默許警方係<strong>唔公開</strong>下用武力使用手則作辯解，變相佢官字兩把口，點講都得。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jvO5wLY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjvO5wLY.png&h=114803ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/11_useful_info/pgo.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Fppp_tc%2F11_useful_info%2Fpgo.html&d=WPnlDqr2f%2BBS7HOcP0JQk8RCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=e70f19e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/11_useful_info/pgo.html</a>"},{"pid":"6c08455af1518d68afc93d42c7cec51e1f4cc33d","tid":1064773,"uid":12468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T19:59:39.000Z","msg":"推"}]}